There is no seal at the pulley, just the grooves on the pulley that 'sling'
the oil back into the case. The leak is most likley coming from the oil pump
cover.

Correct "cheese head" screws are avaliable new here:
http://www.aircooled.net/new-bin/viewproductdetail.php?keyword2=THB0002

